\c 41
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukusiliswa ekuguleni
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Ubusisiwe onanzelela obuthakathaka\x + Zaga 14.21. Mat. 5.7.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* izamkhulula ngosuku lobubi\x + Seb. 12.11.\x*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* izamlondoloza, imgcine ephila; uzabusiswa emhlabeni; kawuyikumnikela entandweni yezitha zakhe.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* izamsekela embhedeni wokugula kwakhe; wena uzaguqula lonke icansi lakhe emkhuhlaneni wakhe\x + Hlab. 20.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Mina ngathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, woba lomusa kimi\x + Hlab. 4.1.\x*, silisa umphefumulo wami, ngoba ngonile kuwe\x + Hlab. 6.2.\x*.
\v 5 Izitha zami zikhuluma okubi ngami \add zisithi\add*: Uzakufa nini, lebizo lakhe lichitheke?
\v 6 Lalapho efika uku\add ngi\add*bona, ukhuluma inkohliso; inhliziyo yakhe izibuthela okubi, esephumile phandle akhulume\x + Hlab. 12.2. 144.8.\x*.
\v 7 Bonke abangizondayo banyenyezelana bemelene lami, bangisongele ukungona.
\v 8 Into embi inamathele kuye; njalo njengoba elele phansi kasayikuvuka\x + 41.3.\x*.
\v 9 Yebo, indoda yobungane bami engiyithembayo\x + Jobe 19.19. Hlab. 55.12,13,20. 2 Sam. 15.12. Jer. 9.4.\x*, ebikade isidla isinkwa sami, ingiphakamisele isithende imelene lami\x + Joha. 13.18. Seb. 1.16.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Kodwa, wena N\nd kosi\nd*, woba lomusa kimi, ungilulamise ukuze ngibaphindisele\x + Hlab. 4.1.\x*.
\v 11 Ngalokhu ngiyazi ukuthi uyangithanda, ngoba isitha sami kasithabanga phezu kwami.
\v 12 Kodwa mina, ungisekele ebuqothweni bami, wangimisa phambi kwakho kuze kube nininini\x + Hlab. 63.8. Hlab. 17.5.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kayibongwe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kusukela phakade kuze kube phakade\x + Luka 1.68.\x*. Ameni, loAmeni\x + Hlab. 72.19. 89.52. 106.48. 150.6.\x*.